</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201001/cda018f2403a45c082b55790fc374745.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">2、鸭肉里放入切好的土豆块、1汤勺米酒、2调羹秘制糟辣椒、2调羹零添加酱油、少许盐、一点姜颗粒、几瓣大蒜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201001/fe685ea669b841da8055328c8295368d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3、充分拌匀腌制15分钟，让鸭肉充分入味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201001/60115719164a42e3ab118479d8332dcd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">编辑</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">4、腌制好之后，把土豆块铺在蒸碗底部。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201001/5023fe9bf3ed4f88a98c94dc2131caf0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">5、然后把泡软的粉丝铺在土豆块上。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201001/06183813b4e4497f9124c1c04870f130.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">6、最后把鸭肉铺在上面。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201001/26b6f73f42644680b95da1e6902a81d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">7、水开上锅蒸，中火蒸45分钟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201001/4b54b752aebe4c02b0aa373647fc7835.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">8、蒸好端出锅，好吃下饭的秘制蒸鸭肉就好了，做法一点不难，学会了中秋节做给家人吃！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201001/792b8534a5f6447396fc20ca60510d7c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
➜鸭肉这样做太香了，不用一滴水，汤汁浓郁咸香味美，比卤鸭还好吃
